{"tid":2489935,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"連儂隧道學生遭內地漢劏肚兼割頸 男生受盡創傷後遺折磨多次嘗試自殺","createTime":"2021-04-15T08:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T09:17:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"296fe01700da29524d4741f67ef7ccb68a6008ff","tid":2489935,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"19歲中六學生前年10月在大埔墟港鐵站連儂隧道附近派發傳單，其間遭雙程證男子以利刀割頸劏肚，男生當場腸臟溢出。雙程證男子原本被控企圖謀殺罪，及後獲控方同意承認蓄意傷人罪，案件今於高等法院處理。法官陳慶偉透露，男生於案發後患上嚴重創傷後壓力症，有自殺念頭，更曾多次嘗試輕生。陳官直言身體創傷可以痊癒，精神受創卻可纏繞終生。<br />\n<br />\n庭上透露，事主患有嚴重的創傷後壓力症候群（PTSD）。陳官謂法庭過往一直低估事主所受的精神或心理創傷，直言身體的創傷相對容易痊癒，但精神或心理所受的傷害卻可纏繞終身，影響深遠。從報告可見，事主為此事受到嚴重的心理困擾。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/JHUONLLCRVCXFDVONGQGJ462XI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FJHUONLLCRVCXFDVONGQGJ462XI%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sJX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=68b4db40\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FJHUONLLCRVCXFDVONGQGJ462XI%2F&h=5235aad6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/JHUONLLCRVCXFDVONGQGJ462XI/</a>"},{"pid":"a2654de8d2338e5e81d7a342af0474c4333524bf","tid":2489935,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油<br />\n要撐下去"},{"pid":"10bdc30a3064378f70b9dcc20d68222c73b70ceb","tid":2489935,"uid":96871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T09:01:33.000Z","msg":"山番"},{"pid":"c5f3ef7353e39c0f2e5a3c9fd26fcd0c45f111cf","tid":2489935,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a2654de8d2338e5e81d7a342af0474c4333524bf","tid":2489935,"uid":377617,"